Annie Fargé https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Annie_Farg%C3%A9 0 Annie Fargé (15 April 1934 – 4 March 2011) was a French actress named "most promising new star in a situation comedy" in 1961 when she played the title role in CBS's Angel. Especially in Europe, she was often credited as "Annie Fargue".
